**Redownload the map if you put it on a public server please, if you see the map bhop_skyscrapers on a server tell the owner to download the fix.( called bhop_skyscrapers_fix )** Speedrun map i made in about 3 weeks with a space/neon style, should be about 1-2 mins long with easy to hard levels possible on every style, although its most fun on autohop with 1000aa This is my first map, so some stuff might be bad Enjoy!
